enableCurrencies(uint16[]).notice: Used to maintain approvals for various currencies, called initially in the constructor

estimateProfit(address,uint256,(uint8,ad.notice: Used for profit estimation off chain

flashLiquidate(address,uint256,(uint8,ad.notice: Primary entry point for the liquidation call

flashLiquidateBatch(address[],uint256[],.notice: Primary entry point for the liquidation call

getOptimalDeleveragingParams(address,add.notice: Used via static call on the liquidation bot to get parameters for liquidation
